    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This example utilizes the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with its original MacPherson strut/multi-link suspension configuration, and the subframe has been inspected for structural integrity. While the exterior shows minor age-appropriate patina, the mechanical components are in excellent working order, offering the visceral feedback and 8,000 RPM redline that define this generation. A mechanically sound specimen for the purist who prioritizes performance over a trailer-queen status.",
