    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained Midnight Blue metallic sedan that perfectly balances luxury and reliability. This vehicle has been my dependable daily driver, and I have spared no expense on its mechanical upkeep. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger bumper\u2014typical for a car of this age but hardly noticeable from a distance. Inside, the tan leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, though there is some light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the premium surround-sound system and the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as it should. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises; I have followed the manufacturer's service schedule religiously, with the most recent oil change and brake pad replacement completed just last month. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, providing a quiet and stable ride on the highway. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner to drive away with total confidence. Full service records are available for review upon request.",
