    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit is paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a functional M-Variable differential lock. Critical enthusiast maintenance has been addressed: the VANOS system has been overhauled for peak timing accuracy, and the rear subframe has been professionally inspected and reinforced. The suspension retains its factory geometry with updated bushings for precise turn-in. While the exterior shows minor road-going character consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical vitals\u2014including the cooling system and rod bearings\u2014are in solid operational order. A pure, analog performance machine with linear power delivery and exceptional chassis feedback.",
